## Formatting Rules

- One persona at a time.
- Real transcripts verbatim; simulated narration marked `[simulated]`.
- Diff format is a table; closure plan is prose with citation.
- Closure tradeoffs always paired with their cost.
- Don't lecture — cite, surface, defer to the user.
